<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٨٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سُنَّتَ اللَّهِ}</span> ... طَرِيَقَتَهُ فِي عَدَمِ قَبُولِ تَوْبَةِ مَنْ عَايَنَ العَذَابَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
